    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160470/extras/2c388298263626a0970ef3477a7711d2.poster.avif?t=1746947895\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160470/extras/2c388298263626a0970ef3477a7711d2.webm?t=1746947895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160470/extras/2c388298263626a0970ef3477a7711d2.mp4?t=1746947895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Condominium》是一款第一人称氛围恐怖游戏。没有廉价的惊吓场景或怪物追逐，也没有解谜元素。你将穿越切萨雷沉睡的记忆。所有意大利的真实场景和独特的资产都是手工制作的，以实现真实的90年代氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160470/extras/5d1e31c27e2828d65df1c2a2394bd713.poster.avif?t=1746947895\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160470/extras/5d1e31c27e2828d65df1c2a2394bd713.webm?t=1746947895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160470/extras/5d1e31c27e2828d65df1c2a2394bd713.mp4?t=1746947895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现为什么切萨雷独自待在这个既熟悉又充满敌意的地方。<br>这栋公寓比表面看起来更加扭曲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心制作的氛围</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逼真的图形</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >90年代意大利风格</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >令人不安的故事情节</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全手工制作的资产</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配音演出</p></li></ul>",
